text: At Early Morning () is a 1965 Russian drama movie directed by Tatyana Lioznova and starring Nikolay Merzlikin, Valeriy Nosik, Nina Nikitina, Aleksandr Petrov, Oleg Zhakov, Olga Bobkova, Ivan Ryzhov. ==Other websites== * Category:1965 drama movies Category:Russian drama movies Category:Movies directed by Tatyana Lioznova
